# ============================================
# NOTES
# ============================================

# This .gitignore is comprehensive for a cryptocurrency project
# Key priorities:
# 1. Never commit private keys, wallets, or seeds
# 2. Never commit PRIVATE-CONFIDENTIAL.md
# 3. Never commit build artifacts (too large)
# 4. Never commit blockchain data (too large)
# 5. Keep source code and documentation
#
# Before committing, always review with: git status
# Double-check: git diff --cached
#
# To add an exception: use ! prefix (like !README.md)
